Package: Rmolt
Type: Package
Title: Graphic visualization of the birds' molt
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Martin BOZON
Date: 2022-05-26
Maintainer: The package maintainer <bozon.etu@gmail.com>
Description: Graphical visualization of the birds' molt to facilitate the creation of molting graph for passerines having 9 (Rmolt(data,9)) or 10 primaries (Rmolt(data,10)), and alos only for the 10 firt primaries (Rmolt(data,"10_0")).
